text: Heteroclytomorpha sexplagiata is a species of beetle in the family Cerambycidae. It was described by Stephan von Breuning in 1939. It is known from the Solomon Islands.BioLib.cz - Heteroclytomorpha sexplagiata. Retrieved on 8 September 2014. ==References== Category:Homonoeini Category:Beetles described in 1939
